      • getPartial

        public java.lang.Boolean getPartial()
        Boolean which indicates whether we need to take snapshot for the entire Application or for subset. By default it is set to false, and consider that snapshot to be created for all array replication groups in an Application. If set to true, volumes list should be provided with volumes one from each Array replication group.
